ckets</a></li>\n</ul>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"other_resources","title":"Other resources","isH3":true,"content":"<ul>\n <li>A <a href=\"https://hacks.mozilla.org/2011/06/a-wall-powered-by-eventsource-and-server-sent-events/\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">Twitter like application</a> powered by server-sent events and <a class=\"link-https external\" href=\"https://github.com/mozilla/webowonder-demos/tree/master/demos/friends%20timeline\" rel=\" noopener\">its code on Github</a>.</li>\n <li><a href=\"https://dsheiko.com/weblog/html5-and-server-sent-events\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">HTML5 and Server-sent events</a></li>\n <li><a href=\"https://rajudasa.blogspot.in/2012/05/html5-server-sent-events-using-aspnet.html\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">Server-sent events using Asp.Net</a></li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"Понятия и применение","id":"понятия_и_применение"},{"text":"Interfaces","id":"interfaces"},{"text":"Examples","id":"examples"},{"text":"Specification","id":"specification"},{"text":"See also","id":"see_also"}],"summary":"По традиции, web-страница должна отправить запрос на сервер, чтобы получить новые данные; это то, как страница получает данные с сервера. Server-sent events дают возможность серверу отправлять новые данные web-странице в любое время, отсылая сообщения web-странице. Такие входящие сообщения могут расцениваться как Events + data внутри web-страницы.","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-10-01T03:41:16.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"Server-sent events","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"Server-sent events","locale":"es","native":"Español"},{"title":"Server-sent events","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"title":"サーバー送信イベント","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"},{"title":"Server-sent events","locale":"ko","native":"한국어"},{"title":"Server-sent events","locale":"pt-BR","native":"Português (do Brasil)"},{"title":"Server-sent events","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)"},{"title":"Server-sent events","loc